<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="landing-page">
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <a href="/"><img src="/img/vibewriter-logo.png" alt="VibeWriter Home" class="logo"></a>
            <h1 class="hero-title">Support Vibes</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="support-content-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-grid">
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>How do I connect my Strava account?</summary>
                    <p>Simply click the "Connect with Strava" button on the homepage. You will be redirected to Strava to authorize the application. Once you approve, you'll be brought back to your dashboard.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>What should I do if my activity titles aren't updating?</summary>
                    <p>First, ensure you have granted the necessary permissions. You can try disconnecting and reconnecting your Strava account from the dashboard. If the issue persists, please check the "Known Issues" section below.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>How is my data used?</summary>
                    <p>We only request permission to view your activities and update their titles. We do not store any of your personal data beyond what is necessary to provide the service. Your privacy is our top priority.</p>
                </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="support-content-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Troubleshooting Guides</h2>
            <div class="faq-grid">
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>How to reconnect your Strava account</summary>
                    <ol class="troubleshooting-steps">
                        <li>Go to your dashboard.</li>
                        <li>Click the "Disconnect Strava" button.</li>
                        <li>Return to the homepage and click "Connect with Strava" again.</li>
                        <li>Follow the prompts to re-authorize the application.</li>
                    </ol>
                </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="support-content-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Report an Issue</h2>
            <div class="faq-grid">
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>Found a bug or have a feature request?</summary>
                    <p>If you've encountered an issue or have an idea for a new feature, please help us improve by <a href="https://github.com/wadewegner/strava-title-generator/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">creating an issue on our GitHub page</a>. Please be as detailed as possible in your report.</p>
                </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %> 